## Security

- âœ… Process isolation for stdio servers
- âœ… Environment variable control
- âœ… No shell injection vulnerabilities
- âœ… Input validation
- âœ… Configurable permissions per server

**Best Practices**:
- Use restricted directories for filesystem access
- Use read-only tokens when possible
- Store secrets in environment variables
- Validate tool inputs before execution
- Review MCP server code before use

